Aug 14 2017 -- v1.4.0
========================================
New
+ Added support for the MLSD FTP command as an alternative to the LIST 
command which provides a standardized format for directory listings

Weid, Nov 12 2014 -- v1.3.1
========================================
Fixed
+ Server error messages are now being captured and returned, rather than
guessing what the error is.

Sun, May 25 2014 -- v1.3.0
========================================
New
+ It is no longer necessary to URL encode paths before making calls to library;
as all paths are now URL encoded internally.
